Key Match Events: India ALL OUT England for 103 in just 16.4 overs and won the match by 68 runs
Kuldeep Yadav and Axar Patel took three wickets each
Axar Patel was crowned as the Player of the Match
Post-Match Reflections: Rohit Sharma expressed pride in the team's resilience after the comeback win
Miscellaneous Highlights: Rain delays led to the game being postponed until the next day
